|Consumer Web Portal             |Next.js 15 (Static/SSR)                     |Hosted free di Vercel                                                                                                                  |
|Backend                         |Supabase                                    |PostgreSQL, Auth, Storage, Realtime, Edge Functions                                                                                    |
|AI                              |Google Gemini 2.5 Flash                     |Scan nota, generate kontrak/undangan text. Free tier: 15 RPM, 1000 RPD. Paid: $0.30/$2.50 per 1M tokens. Model string: gemini-2.5-flash|
|Styling                         |NativeWind                                  |Tailwind for RN                                                                                                                        |
|State                           |Zustand + TanStack Query                    |                                                                                                                                       |
|Forms                           |React Hook Form + Zod                       |                                                                                                                                       |
|Navigation                      |Expo Router                                 |File-based                                                                                                                             |
|Push Notifications              |Expo Notifications                          |Provider + Consumer                                                                                                                    |
|Image                           |Expo Image Picker + Camera                  |                                                                                                                                       |
|PDF                             |expo-print + expo-sharing                   |                                                                                                                                       |
|QR                              |react-native-qrcode-svg + expo-camera (scan)|                                                                                                                                       |
|Charts                          |victory-native                              |                                                                                                                                       |
|Icons                           |lucide-react-native                         |                                                                                                                                       |
|Auth                            |Supabase Auth                               |Google + Phone OTP                                                                                                                     |
|Offline                         |AsyncStorage + queue                        |Basic offline support                                                                                                                  |
|Realtime                        |Supabase Realtime                           |Provider update -> Consumer instant                                                                                                    |
|Deep Linking                    |Expo Linking + Universal Links              |berest.id/xx/xx -> app if installed                                                                                                    |

### Gemini 2.5 Flash - Why This Model

- Gemini 2.0 Flash RETIRED per Juni 2026. Jangan pakai.
- Gemini 2.5 Flash = stable production model, free tier generous (15 RPM, ~1000 RPD), multimodal (bisa OCR scan nota/KTP), harga paid tier sangat murah ($0.30 input / $2.50 output per 1M tokens).
- Gemini 3 Flash Preview = lebih baru tapi masih preview, bisa berubah. Gak recommended untuk production app.
- Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite = backup option kalau butuh lebih murah untuk simple text tasks.
- Model string untuk API call: `gemini-2.5-flash`

