## 15. CONSUMER WEB PORTAL ROUTES

All routes: **berest.id/[code]/[slug]**

```
berest.id/                              -> Landing page + download app
berest.id/lb/[order_code]              -> Order/laundry status (Lapak)
berest.id/gp/[student_slug]            -> Student/parent portal (Lapak - Guru)
berest.id/bb/[biz_slug]               -> Queue/storefront (Lapak - Jasa)
berest.id/wk/[biz_slug]               -> Product catalog (Lapak - Warung)
berest.id/kh/[tenant_code]            -> Tenant portal (Sewa - Kos/Hunian)
berest.id/rn/[rental_code]            -> Rental status (Sewa - Rental)
berest.id/rt/[member_code]            -> Member portal (Warga - RT)
berest.id/rt/laporan                   -> Public financial report (Warga)
berest.id/ms/[code]                    -> Mesjid portal (Warga - Mesjid)
berest.id/ms/laporan                   -> Public infaq report (Warga)
berest.id/hj/[event_slug]             -> Invitation page (Hajat)
berest.id/hj/[event_slug]/[guest_code] -> Personalized RSVP (Hajat)
```

Semua route: static-generated atau server-rendered. Gak perlu install. Gak perlu login untuk view. Actions (RSVP, confirm payment) butuh simple verification (kode + no HP).

Setiap halaman web punya **smart banner**: “Download beRest untuk notifikasi real-time” dengan deep link ke Play Store. Jika app sudah terinstall, deep link buka langsung ke screen yang relevan di app.

