## 16. PHASED BUILD STRATEGY

### Phase 0: Foundation (Week 1-3)

Setup project, Supabase, auth (Google + Phone OTP), shared layer (contacts, financial dashboard, reminder engine, WA share engine, notification system), UI component library, tab navigation, module selection onboarding, **consumer connection system** (kode koneksi, auto-detect nomor HP, QR scan), **consumer dashboard shell** (connected providers list, empty states).

Quality gate: app boots, register/login works, module selection works, provider AND consumer onboarding both work, consumer can input connection code, empty state per module.

### Phase 1: Module Warga - MVP (Week 4-8)

Alasan build pertama: paling simple secara teknis, viral coefficient paling tinggi.

Scope:

- Provider: Kas & Iuran (full CRUD + laporan + share link) + Pengumuman (basic)
- Consumer web: berest.id/rt/[code] (warga cek status + laporan publik)
- Consumer app: warga dashboard (iuran status, pengumuman, jadwal), upload bukti bayar, push notification
- Reminder pembayaran (provider -> consumer via push + WA)

Quality gate: bendahara kelola 30 warga, warga cek status via web DAN app, laporan transparan via link, push notification consumer works.

### Phase 2: Module Lapak - Mode Pedagang (Week 9-12)

Scope:

- Provider: Mode Pedagang (catat penjualan + pengeluaran + profit)
- Consumer web: berest.id/wk/[slug] (katalog mini)
- Consumer app: favorite stores, order history
- Financial dashboard integration (Warga + Lapak aggregated)

Quality gate: pedagang catat penjualan 3 detik/transaksi, consumer browse katalog via web, dashboard aggregated works.

### Phase 3: Module Sewa - Properti (Week 13-17)

Scope:

- Provider: Kos/kontrakan (unit + penghuni + billing), Kontrak template (Gemini 2.5 Flash)
- Consumer web: berest.id/kh/[code] (tenant cek tagihan + lapor masalah)
- Consumer app: tenant dashboard (tagihan, kontrak, maintenance request), upload bukti bayar, push notification
- Payment tracking + reminder

Quality gate: pemilik kos kelola 10 kamar, penghuni cek via web DAN app, maintenance request flow works.

### Phase 4: Module Lapak - Mode Advanced (Week 18-22)

Scope:

- Provider: Mode Laundry (order + status), Mode Guru/Pelatih (murid + jadwal + absensi + tagihan), Mode Jasa Umum (antrian QR)
- Consumer web: berest.id/lb/[code] (laundry status), berest.id/gp/[code] (murid portal), berest.id/bb/[slug] (antrian)
- Consumer app: multi-provider tracking (laundry + guru + antrian all in 1 dashboard), real-time status updates via Supabase Realtime, push notifications
- Customer Database (cross-mode)

Quality gate: laundry 20 order/hari, guru 15 murid, barbershop antrian digital, consumer app tracks all real-time.

### Phase 5: Module Hajat (Week 23-27)

Scope:

- Provider: Undangan digital (templates + Gemini 2.5 Flash generate text), RSVP + guest manager, Amplop tracker
- Consumer web: berest.id/hj/[slug] (invitation page + RSVP form)
- Consumer app: incoming invitations dashboard, RSVP via app, amplop suggestion, hajatan calendar
- Deep linking: undangan link -> app if installed -> direct to invitation screen

Quality gate: bikin undangan nikahan, kirim ke 200 tamu, RSVP works web + app, amplop tracker works.

### Phase 6: Sewa Rental + Polish + Launch (Week 28-32)

Scope:

- Provider: Rental items management, before/after photo
- Consumer web + app: rental status
- Warga Jadwal & Giliran sub-module + portal
- AI scan features (nota, kontrak) via Gemini 2.5 Flash
- Advanced analytics semua module
- Export PDF/CSV
- Subscription/paywall logic
- Web-to-app conversion optimization (smart banners, deep links)
- Performance optimization
- Full regression test
- Play Store listing prep

Quality gate: semua module OK, semua web portals live, semua consumer app features work, app performant, ready for public launch.

